---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="隱私權政策 | 文森遊戲"
  description="文森遊戲網站隱私權政策，說明 Google Analytics、Cookie 等資料使用方式。"
>
  <Navigation />
  <main class="privacy-page">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="privacy-header">
        <h1>隱私權政策</h1>
        <p class="privacy-subtitle">Privacy Policy</p>
        <p class="updated">最後更新 Last Updated：2026 年 5 月 29 日</p>
      </header>

      <div class="privacy-body">

        <!-- 中文 -->
        <section>
          <h2>一、前言</h2>
          <p>歡迎使用文森遊戲（網址：vincent2077.com）。本隱私權政策說明本網站如何收集、使用及保護您的相關資訊。使用本網站即表示您同意本政策內容。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>二、收集的資訊</h2>
          <p>本網站<strong>不會</strong>主動要求您提供個人身份資料（如姓名、電子郵件、電話等）。</p>
          <p>然而，本網站使用以下第三方服務，可能自動收集部分資訊：</p>

          <h3>Google Analytics</h3>
          <p>本網站使用 Google Analytics 分析網站流量與使用行為，收集資訊包含瀏覽器類型、作業系統、參照網址、瀏覽頁面與停留時間、大致地理位置（國家／城市層級）及裝置類型。上述資料以匿名聚合方式處理，無法用於識別個人身份。詳見 <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google 隱私權政策</a>。</p>

          <h3>YouTube 嵌入內容</h3>
          <p>部分頁面可能嵌入 YouTube 影片。當您播放影片時，YouTube 可能收集相關資料，詳見 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube 隱私權政策</a>。</p>

          <h3>整合行銷工具盒</h3>
          <p>本網站連結至<a href="https://vincentcodex.github.io/Marketing-Tools/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">整合行銷工具盒</a>，該工具所有運算皆於使用者瀏覽器本地完成，不上傳任何資料至伺服器。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>三、Cookie 使用</h2>
          <p>本網站透過 Google Analytics 使用 Cookie 以追蹤匿名使用統計。您可透過瀏覽器設定停用 Cookie，或安裝 <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics 選擇退出附加元件</a>來拒絕追蹤。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>四、第三方連結</h2>
          <p>本網站可能包含連結至外部網站（如 YouTube、GitHub 等）。本網站對這些外部網站的隱私權實踐不負任何責任，建議您閱讀各網站的隱私權政策。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>五、資料安全</h2>
          <p>本網站託管於 Cloudflare 及 GitHub Pages，並透過 HTTPS 加密傳輸。本網站不儲存任何使用者個人資料。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>六、政策異動</h2>
          <p>本隱私權政策可能不定期更新，更新後將在本頁標示最新日期，建議您定期查閱。</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>七、聯絡方式</h2>
          <p>如有任何疑問，歡迎透過以下方式聯繫：</p>
          <ul>
            <li>YouTube 頻道：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@VincentGame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">youtube.com/@VincentGame</a></li>
            <li>個人網站：<a href="https://vincent2077.com">vincent2077.com</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <hr />

        <!-- English -->
        <section>
          <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>Welcome to VincentGame (vincent2077.com). This Privacy Policy explains how the Site collects, uses, and protects information when you visit. By using this Site, you agree to the terms described below.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. Information Collected</h2>
          <p>This Site does <strong>not</strong> actively collect personally identifiable information (such as name, email address, or phone number).</p>
          <p>However, the following third-party services may automatically collect certain data:</p>

          <h3>Google Analytics</h3>
          <p>This Site uses Google Analytics to analyze traffic and user behavior. Data collected includes browser type, operating system, referring URL, pages visited, time spent, approximate geographic location, and device type. All data is processed anonymously and cannot identify individuals. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

          <h3>YouTube Embedded Content</h3>
          <p>Some pages may embed YouTube videos. When you play a video, YouTube may collect data per <a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

          <h3>Marketing Toolbox</h3>
          <p>This Site links to the <a href="https://vincentcodex.github.io/Marketing-Tools/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marketing Toolbox</a>. All processing occurs locally in your browser — no data is sent to any server.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
          <p>This Site uses cookies via Google Analytics for anonymous usage statistics. You may disable cookies in your browser settings or install the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Add-on</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>This Site may contain links to external websites (e.g., YouTube, GitHub). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their policies.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
          <p>This Site is hosted on Cloudflare and GitHub Pages, served over HTTPS. No personal user data is stored.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. The revision date will be noted at the top of this page.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Contact</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>YouTube: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@VincentGame" target="_blank" rel="noopener">youtube.com/@VincentGame</a></li>
            <li>Website: <a href="https://vincent2077.com">vincent2077.com</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + 3rem) 2rem 6rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .privacy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .privacy-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .privacy-body section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .privacy-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .privacy-body h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 1rem 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .privacy-body p,
  .privacy-body li {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .privacy-body ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-body a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .privacy-body a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .privacy-body hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-page {
      padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 1.5rem);
    }
  }
</style>